high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the coffee machine in the kitchen
Pick up the white mug from the coffee machine
Turn left and approach the microwave on the kitchen counter
Warm the mug in the microwave and remove it
Turn left and walk around the fridge to the wooden shelf near a door
Put the mug down on the third shelf from bottom
anns.task_desc: Put the white mug on the wooden shelf

high_descs: Pick up the mug from the coffee machine.
Bring the mug to the microwave.
Heat the mug in the microwave.
Bring the mug to the wooden shelves.
Put the mug on the wooden shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug on the wooden shelf.

high_descs: Turn around and head towards the coffee maker.
Pick up the cup from the coffee maker.
Turn left and head towards the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the cup in it, heat it up, and take the cup out of microwave.
Turn left, walk past the fridge, and then turn left towards the wooden shelf on your right.
Place the cup on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place the heated cup on the top shelf.
